divs: Sighting DetailsI was walking my dog here in Seminole and I was distracted by a craft above me wit HUGE lights in the sky. I looked up, and just up in the sky was a triangle UFO with FOUR LIGHTS. I was on the phone at the time with a friend and I said, "i think I am seeing a UFO above me". She replied that I should take a photo. I pointed my i-phone at it a second later and was able to get these two shots as it was disappearing. When I blow these up you can clearly see a TRIANGLE ship with a huge lead light and three tail lights.
